 <H1>Online Validation: Motivation</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Classical system design depends on off-line testing/validation of hardware designs
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Huge cost/ effort for complex designs, many errors get through
<LI>CAD tools / Compilers often generate erroneous code (see errata lists!)
<LI>Correct by construction doesnï¿½t work (at least not yet!).
</UL></UL><UL>
